title: Truth by Calvin Klein for Women, Eau De Parfum Spray, 3.4 Ounce
description: Launched by the design house of Calvin Klein in 2000, TRUTH PERFUME is classified as a refreshing, oriental, woody fragrance. This feminine scent possesses a blend of fresh, natural rich woods that react to individual skin chemistry. It is recommended for casual wear.

title: Nautica Classic for Men by Nautica 3.4 oz 100ml EDT Spray
description: Introduced in 1992, Nautica features watery florals and tones of aromatic woods. Its recommended use is for daytime occasions.When applying any fragrance please consider that there are several factors which can affect the natural smell of your skin and, in turn, the way a scent smells on you.  For instance, your mood, stress level, age, body chemistry, diet, and current medications may all alter the scents you wear.  Similarly, factor such as dry or oily skin can even affect the amount of time a fragrance will last after being applied

title: Guess Seductive by Guess 2.5 oz 75 ml EDT Spray
description: Seductive by Guess is a fragrance for women. Seductive is a new fragrance and it was introduced in 2010. The nose behind this fragrance is Veronique Nyberg. Top notes are bergamot, black currant and pear; middle notes are jasmine, african orange flower and orris root; base notes are vanille, olibanum and cashmere wood.
